Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 25, 2017 8:17 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. is a privately owned real estate investment trust launched and managed by Lightstone Value Plus REIT III LLC. The fund invests in the real estate markets of United States. It invests primarily in the hotels. Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. was formed on October 5, 2012 and is based in Lakewood, New Jersey.


1985 Cedar Bridge AvenueSuite 1Lakewood, NJ 08701United StatesFounded in 2012



lightstonecapitalmarkets.com/reits#openreit-12







Key Executives for Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc.




Mr. David Lichtenstein


      	Chief Executive Officer and Chairman of the Board
      


