Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. Key Developments

Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Six Months Ended June 30, 2016
Mar 28 17
Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the six months ended June 30, 2016. For the period, the company reported revenues of USD 2,774,475 against USD 2,783,155 a year ago. Operating income was USD 706,413 against USD 880,814 a year ago. Net income was USD 415,679 against USD 577,880 a year ago. Net cash provided by operating activities was USD 610,555 against USD 831,100 a year ago. Purchase of real estate was USD 85,842 against USD 35,868 a year ago.


