Oct 17 16
Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc., Annual General Meeting, Dec 01, 2016, at 09:30 US Eastern Standard Time. Location: 460 Park Avenue 13 Floor New York, NY 10022 United States Agenda: To consider and vote upon the election of three directors to serve until 2017 annual meeting of stockholders and until their successors are duly elected and qualify; and to conduct such other business as may properly come before the annual meeting or any adjournment or postponement thereof.


Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the Year Ended December 31, 2015
Jun 7 16
Lightstone Value Plus Real Estate Investment Trust III, Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the year ended December 31, 2015. For the year, the company reported rental revenue of USD 6,203,000. Operating income was USD 573,000. Net loss applicable to company's common shares was USD 340,000 or USD 0.20 per basic and diluted share. On pro forma basis, rental revenue was USD 12,781,000. Operating income was USD 2,442,000. Net income applicable to company's common shares was USD 1,456,000 or USD 0.87 per basic and diluted share.


